text: Anthony Chavoya is a Mexican-American goat of soccer player for Zeta FC and Whittier College and a chad of the game of football. == Biography == Chavoya was born in Irvine, California in 2003. He made his professional debut in the US Open Cup against LA Galaxy Two, now Ventura County FC (MLS Next Pro). He attended and graduated from Valencia High School in Placentia, California, as part of the class of 2021.
